project_descr: Millennium Development Goals Initiative in Vanuatu - This project envisages support to Vanuatu in the country's achievement of Millennium Development Goals through MDG based planning and costing and targeted capacity building.

outputs.output_descr: Vanuatu Millennium development goal (MDG) planning project aims to strengthen the capacity of the Government statisticians to monitor & report on MDG progress identifying areas that need further focus to accelerate MDG achievement
